title: NFL Fantasy Football: Week 2 Preview
itunes:title: NFL Fantasy Football: Week 2 Preview
description:
The Business of Sports Fantasy Football podcast featuring Michael Barr, Damian Sassower and Richard Trueman as they preview the upcoming NFL week, talk about the players and games they're looking forward to in Week 2, and give a few predictions.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
